<li><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/CharacterizationTropes" title="Main/CharacterizationTropes">Characterization</a></li>
<li><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Characters" title="Main/Characters">Characters</a></li>
